Sentencas: Symmetric half cell structures of highly epitaxial PrBaCo2O5+delta (PBCO)/Gd0.8Ce0.2.2O2:Y0.08Zr0.92 O-2/PrBaCo2O5+delta thin films were designed and fabricated on (001) LaAlO3.
Titulo: Ultrafast oxygen exchange kinetics on highly epitaxial PrBaCo2O5+δ thin films

Sentencas: Microstructural studies indicate that the multilayer films have excellent single-crystal quality and epitaxial nature.
Titulo: Ultrafast oxygen exchange kinetics on highly epitaxial PrBaCo2O5+δ thin films

Sentencas: The electrochemical impedance spectroscopy measurements reveal that the PBCO film electrodes have a polarization resistance as low as 0.109 Omega cm(2) at 597 degrees C in air and an ultrafast surface exchange coefficient (0.006 cm/s at 598 degrees C) with low activation energy (0.77 eV).
Titulo: Ultrafast oxygen exchange kinetics on highly epitaxial PrBaCo2O5+δ thin films

Sentencas: The low polarization resistance and rapid surface oxygen exchange kinetics suggest that the PBCO can be an excellent cathode material for intermediate-temperature solid oxide fuel cells.
Titulo: Ultrafast oxygen exchange kinetics on highly epitaxial PrBaCo2O5+δ thin films
